{{作品名稱|name=''Blue Jasmine''|hk=情迷藍茉莉|tw=藍色茉莉|equiv-cn=tw}}是一部2013年[[伍迪·艾伦|伍迪·艾伦]]编剧并执导的美国剧情片<ref>{{cite news|last=Burkeman|first=Oliver|title=Woody Allen: 'To have been a lead character in a juicy scandal doesn't bother me'|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2012/sep/13/woody-allen-juicy-scandal|accessdate=January 9, 2013|newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=September 13, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Greene|first=Andy|title=Andrew Dice Clay's Surprising Comeback and Why He Won't Clean Up His Act|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/andrew-dice-clays-surprising-comeback-and-why-he-wont-stop-saying-fag-20121228|accessdate=January 9, 2013|newspaper=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]|date=December 28, 2012}}</ref><ref name="NYT">{{cite news|last=Itzkoff|first=Dave|title=Woody Allen Names His New Movie ‘Blue Jasmine’|url=http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2013/01/08/woody-allen-names-his-new-movie-blue-jasmine/|accessdate=January 8, 2013|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=January 8, 2013}}</ref>，[[凯特·布兰切特|凯特·布兰切特]]、[[莎莉·霍金斯|莎莉·霍金斯]]和[[亚历克·鲍德温|亚历克·鲍德温]]主演。2013年7月26日在[[纽约市|纽约市]]和[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]有限上映<ref>{{cite news|last=Busis|first=Hillary|title='Before Midnight,' latest from Woody Allen & Pedro Almodovar get release dates|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/02/07/before-midnight-release-date/|accessdate=February 9, 2013|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=February 7, 2013}}</ref>，英国于9月27日上映<ref name=pb1sep>{{cite news|title=Film highlights of autumn 2013: from Diana to The Selfish Giant|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2013/sep/01/best-films-autumn-2013-diana-selfish-giant|accessdate=September 7, 2013|newspaper=The Guardian|date=September 1, 2013|author=Peter Bradshaw}}</ref>。女主角布兰切特获得超過30座影評人協會獎及[[第71屆金球獎|第71屆金球獎]]、第20屆[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]、[[第67屆英國電影學院獎|第67屆英國電影學院獎]]和[[第86届奥斯卡金像奖|第86届奥斯卡金像奖]][[奥斯卡最佳女主角|最佳女主角]]奖<ref>[http://www.cna.com.tw/topic/popular/4336-1/201403030045-1.aspx 凱特布蘭琪 奧斯卡封后] {{Wayback|url=http://www.